U2      u2_g_MtrxSrch_lt(const U4  u4_a_INST, const ST_MTRX_SRCH * const st_ap_SRCH);

/*--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/* Note:                                                                                                        */
/*                                                                                                              */
/* u2_g_MtrxSrch_lt:                                                                                            */
/*    It is a mtrxsrch limited to 1word using the instruction of G3M.                                           */
/*    This improves the speed of exploration.                                                                   */
/*    The difference from the "u2_g_mtrxsrch" is as follows.                                                    */
/*      1. There isn't "u2_a_IDX_STA", which is the first argument of the "u2_g_mtrxsrch".                      */
/*         As a result, the search start idx becomes "0".                                                       */
/*      2. The size of the value that can be search is 1word.                                                   */
/*         If you want to search for a size larger than 1word, use "u2_g_mtrxsrch".                             */
/*--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

